=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex68 ===

DESCRIPTION: A dark mixed sound, with fm_or_inharmonic oscillator character around 492 Hz, featuring punchy attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, and filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: dark
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: moderate
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 492.4578
  harmonic_decay_rate: -3.9849
  harmonic_regularity: 0.5887
  pitch_clarity: 21.1796
  inharmonicity: 0.3866
  type: fm_or_inharmonic
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -24.1752
  resonance_freq: 667.5293

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Tour of UGens Example 68
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Guides/Tour_of_UGens.html
// Tags: Tour_of_UGens, Guides
// ---
// --- Example 68 ---
{ Blip.ar(Gate.ar(LFNoise2.ar(40), LFPulse.ar(1)) * 400 + 500, 4, 0.2) }.play;
